name: Jamison McDermott

last_movies.title: 怪物：梅内德斯兄弟的故事

introduction: Jamison McDermott is an American actress, director, producer, and writer originally from Chicago, IL. She moved to Los Angeles when she was selected as 1 of 16 students worldwide for the highly esteemed Professional On-Camera Acting Program within the Television and Film School at UCLA. She has trained under notable actors, directors, and casting directors from LA, NY, Atlanta and Chicago. In 2017, Jamison founded 715 Productions, Inc. where she writes, produces, and directs a range of content. Her work has been featured on channels such as MTV worldwide, NBC, Xfinity On Demand and more.
